/>","description":"Displays a hierarchical tree of categories/subcategories and always shows a persistent 'Uncategorized' node (at the top or bottom as specified in config). The 'Uncategorized' node uses a distinct icon (e.g., maple leaf with reggae colors) and is always visible and selectable, not just on initial load. When selected, emits itemSelected with its special ID. Handles expand/collapse, selection, and keyboard navigation. Visually highlights the active node, including the 'Uncategorized' node. Integrates Canadian and Rasta color motifs (especially on the 'Uncategorized' node). Handles empty states and passes hierarchical state for expanded/collapsed nodes. All interactions are accessible by mouse and keyboard.","statePath":"sidebar","components":[{"placeholder":"SUB_CHILD_COMPONENT_1","programmaticName":"CategoryTreeNode","description":"Represents a single category, subcategory, or the special 'Uncategorized' node. Handles expand/collapse (if it has children), selection/highlighting, and visual cues (icon, color) for the 'Uncategorized' node. Emits selection and expand/collapse events. Uses appropriate Canadian/Rasta color accents. Handles keyboard navigation (Arrow keys, Enter/Space for select, etc).","statePath":"treeNode","components":[],"componentCode":"function CategorySidebar({ data, config, userState, onEvent, styles, callbacks, utilities, statePath, selectedCategoryID }) {
    // <<CATEGORY_TREE_NODE>>

    // ---- Canadian/Rasta Theming ----
    // Theme accents
    const CANADA_RED = '#d32d27';
    const RASTA_GREEN = '#388e3c';
    const RASTA_YELLOW = '#ffd600';
    const RASTA_RED = '#d32d27';
    const CANADA_WHITE = '#fff';
    const LEAF_EMOJI = '??';
